  "keyFeatures": [
    "Declarative game development using Svelte 5 components with PixiJS 8 rendering",
    "Event-driven architecture via bookEvents and emitterEvents for game state management",
    "Finite state machine (XState) for betting and game flow control",
    "Monorepo structure with TurboRepo for modular, reusable packages",
    "Storybook integration for isolated component and game-mode testing",
    "Built-in Spine animation, SpriteSheet, and particle support via pixi-svelte",
    "Responsive layout system with canvas size and device type awareness",
    "Internationalization (i18n) support with Lingui",
    "Sample games: lines, cluster, scatter, ways, price, number-picker"
  ],
